Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=10}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O-Outro relatório do portão principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:15.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é {\i1}dessa{\i0} vez?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:24.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um grupo suspeito numa carruagem de monstros\Nacabou de pular a cerca frontal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:29.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, mandem reforços!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:31.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, mandem–
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:41.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:43.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porteiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:44.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Responda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que tá acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que houve, Nico Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:30.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês estão prontos?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:33.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como estão seus ferimentos?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou ficar bem, porque...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou o Sogeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:47.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Em quatro minutos, o trem marítimo\N{\i1}Rocketman{\i0} vai avançar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:01.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com licença, mas... por favor, me deixem passar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:06.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mesmo pedindo educadamente...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"não" significa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,não!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:14.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,se preparem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pirata atrevido!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:21.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ally Robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Isso é jogo sujo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não dá pra atacar ele assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que truque infantil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se segurem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:45.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ally Robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:47.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:49.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ally Robot Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe muito, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já chega!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Suas costas estão totalmente abertas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:25.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Derrubem ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:27.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É só um homem desarmado!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:53.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como é que ele é tão ágil assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu tô com pressa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:57.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais gente vem depois!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:58.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Falou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:08.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei... para!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:11.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele passou! Rápido! Entrem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:13.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tá na ilha principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:15.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chefe, aqui é o portão da ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:19.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O Ch-Chapéu de Palha Luffy\Npisou na ilha principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Vocês deixaram ele entrar na ilha principal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que diabos tá acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que o Oimo e o Kashi tão fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:29.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele derrubou eles também?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:33.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não, senhor! É meio da\Nnoite agora, então...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}eles provavelmente tão dormindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é hora de dormir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:39.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vão acordar eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:41.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acordem todos os guardas da ilha principal também!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:47.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É só um invasor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:50.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tem motivo pra tanto\Nalvoroço, né, Chefe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:53.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês têm a gente.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não seja ridículo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:07:01.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esta é a Ilha Judiciária, a sagrada\Nentrada simbólica do Governo Mundial.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:07.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qualquer idiota devia saber\No que significa invadir esse lugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:13.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E mesmo assim, ele invadiu a ilha principal\Nsó pra recuperar um único membro da tripulação!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:16.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É uma vergonha!\NQuem ele pensa que somos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:20.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Malditos Chapéus de Palha e seus cúmplices!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porteiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:25.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Explique o que tá acontecendo no portão principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, porteiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:29.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quantos inimigos são?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde eles estão?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:34.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Portão principal, câmbio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ei, o que houve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:41.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Portão principal, responda!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Rope Action...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:47.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Figure-of-Eight Knot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:51.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Bazooka Bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:55.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não devíamos gastar munição ainda!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entrem pelas portas laterais! Abram o portão!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não deixem eles abrir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:07.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Saiam do caminho!\N– Saiam do caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:08.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mozu! Pega o lado esquerdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô nessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como se eu fosse deixar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:15.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Opa! Cresceu um pelo do meu nariz!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Presta atenção!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:22.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Valeu demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:32.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Keel Breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:43.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os portões já tão destrancados?!\NMozu?! Kiwi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:48.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Demolição de navios é trabalho da Família Franky.\NEntão abrir fechaduras é...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Destrancado desse lado!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:53.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desse lado também!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:59.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza então! Abram o portão, Mighty Destroyers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:08.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não deixem eles abrir! Defendam a qualquer custo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:10.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Saiam! Vocês tão no caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:27.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rápido, passem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:35.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Atravessamos o primeiro portão!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:41.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nossa! Que diabo é esse buraco enorme?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é hora de ficar olhando!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:45.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Continuem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:49.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mantenham o curso e cheguem ao portão da ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É uma cachoeira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:55.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Conseguimos!\N– Conseguimos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:58.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, pessoal! Aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me ajudem com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:11.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kashi! Oimo! Acordem agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:16.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O p-portão principal foi\Narrombado por invasores!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:23.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele disse que o portão principal foi arrombado, Oimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:25.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:29.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não é bom, Kashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não quero levantar...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:36.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,...mas é nosso trabalho. Vamos nessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:40.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Certo!\N– Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu não dormi o suficiente.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vou me livrar deles rápido e voltar pra cama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oimo também.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:08.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,G-G-Gigantes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:13.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não sei por que vocês vieram até aqui,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas sugiro que deem meia volta\Nantes que a gente esmague vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:17.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Né, Oimo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:20.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, Kashi. Oimo concorda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:24.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos esmagar vocês, até os ossos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:27.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Gigantes guardando o portão?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não é justo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:33.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles são enormes! Fazem nossos\NMighty Destroyers parecerem minúsculos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:36.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, voltem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:38.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou deixar vocês passarem por esse portão!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oimo também não!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lá vêm eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:45.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não importa o inimigo, fiquem firmes, Família Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:47.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é pelo Irmão!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:51.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sim!\N– Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:55.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, vocês entendem, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:56.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:58.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:05.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se não a gente, quem mais poderia enfrentá-los?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:10.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desmontar navios nos fez\N{\q2}fortes o bastante pra enfrentar esses gigantes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:12.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Destroyers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:39.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,N-Nossos Mighty Destroyers foram...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Foi tão rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:46.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós nascemos guerreiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:51.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O sangue nas nossas veias é diferente\Ndo de humanos grandes demais.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:55.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou deixar uma pessoa sequer passar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:56.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oimo também não!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:59.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,N-N-Não amoleçam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:01.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não desistam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:05.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É isso aí! O Grande Irmão Franky tá\Ndo outro lado daquele portão!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:12.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mostrem uma luta digna\Ndo nome do Irmão, Família Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:22.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Chapéu de Palha Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quantos amigos você trouxe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:30.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São 10.000 soldados em Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, eu tô sozinho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E você tá no meu caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:50.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mostrem uma luta digna\Ndo nome do Irmão, Família Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não desistam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:00.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Abram caminho pro {\i1}Rocketman{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:09.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Arrombem o portão!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:16.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente não vai deixar\Nnem uma formiga passar por esse portão!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Destroyers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:30.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Vocês já derrubaram\Nalguns dos nossos mais fortes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zambai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kiwi! Mozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Galley-La!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:51.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa o atraso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:55.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Trocar Sodom e Gomorrah\Npro modo terrestre demorou mais que o esperado!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zambai! Os Destroyers...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:00.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:04.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas não dá pra parar pra consertar eles agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:10.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra chegar onde o Irmão tá,\Na gente tem que abrir esse portão custe o que custar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:13.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:18.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos desequilibrar ele, Mozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:21.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendido, Kiwi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:31.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}– Hull Dismantler Slash!\N– Hull Dismantler Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Rope Action...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:39.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Timber Hitch Tug!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai, ai, ai, ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:15:59.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tilestone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:14.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai, ai, ai, ai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:16.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Trunnel Lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:17.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seus ratos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:34.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou esmagar vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:50.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como vocês ousam...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só falta mais um, galera!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:02.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sim!\N– Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, qual é a situação atual?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:16.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Senhor, Kashi e Oimo estão cuidando deles\Nagora, em frente ao portão da ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:18.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não prevemos nenhum problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:19.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, vocês capturaram o Chapéu de Palha,\No invasor da ilha principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:25.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bom... é que...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:29.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}isso é só uma estimativa,\Nmas são cerca de 400...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:30.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quatrocentos?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Do que você tá falando?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nossas baixas, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:44.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hã?! Nossas baixas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tá dizendo que 400 guardas caíram?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:49.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pode somar mais uns cem...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uh, desculpe. Preciso revisar essa estimativa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:56.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Assim espero!\NNossos guardas não são tão fracos assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não tem como ser tantos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:01.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Se tem baixas,\Nreportem com precisão!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:10.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm... Muito bem. Aqui vai o relatório.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:12.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Até o momento, o número de baixas é cinc–
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Gah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:18.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cinco guardas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:20.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Então na verdade foram só cinco guardas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:23.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Qual {\i0}é{\i1}! Vocês não conseguem\Nnem fazer um relatório direito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:27.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quinh... entos... guar...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:33.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ao invés de lutar, o Chapéu de Palha Luffy\Ntá só correndo pela ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:35.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, isso é natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:38.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ninguém é burro o bastante\Npra enfrentar tantos guardas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:42.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É só questão de tempo até ele ser capturado.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:45.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bem-vindos de volta, senhores e senhora.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:49.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chefe, o grupo do Sr. Lucci chegou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:52.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles voltaram?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:53.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixem eles entrar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Sogeking...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:00.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, isso doeu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:06.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como eu uso esse bastão de ar frio?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:08.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Deixa eu ver...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:14.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Agora, pessoal! É hora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:18.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vamos nessa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:21.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles já devem ter aberto\Nos dois portões.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:24.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Avancem! Avancem!
Comment: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:23.39,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Comment: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:24.98,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:29.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Homem samurai! Cuida da cerca de ferro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixa comigo.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=11}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=12}============================SIGNS AND TITLE=========================
